ProjectBubble,is,a,web,based,project,management,tool,designed,to,save,businesses,time,and,streamline,the,management,process,The,service,allows,users,to,set,budgets,for,projects,break,projects,up,into,smaller,tasks,assign,tasks,to,employees,invite,them,to,join,project,groups,and,also,track,project,time,as,tasks,are,being,completed,using,a,web,interface,The,ProjectBubble,API,using,REST,calls,and,returning,data,in,several,formats,allows,users,to,upload,and,download,segments,of,data,from,projects,The,documentation,is,also,available,to,develop,applications,around,the,ProjectBubble,platform